title: See full schedule for Symphony on the Prairie 2017
text:
See full schedule for Symphony on the Prairie 2017 Allison Carter , allison.carter@indystar.com 11:04 a.m. ET Feb. 22, 2017 Buy Photo Concertgoers dance at the front of the stage at Conner Prairie during the Marsh Symphony on the Prairie: Classical Mystery Tour - Music of the Beatles, Aug. 13, 2011. (D. Kevin Elliott / For the Star) (Photo: Kevin Elliott/IndyStar) Buy Photo 466 CONNECT COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Indianapolis Symphony Orchestra's popular Symphony on the Prairie series, held at Conner Prairie in Fishers, has announced its schedule for 2017. Here's what you can expect: 
Beethoven's Fifth 
Friday, June 16, 8:00 p.m.— Teacher's Night Saturday, June 17, 8:00 p.m. 
One of These Nights -- A Tribute to the Eagles 
Friday, June 23, 8:00 p.m. 
Feeling Groovy -- Remembering the Summer of Love 
Saturday, June 24, 8:00 p.m. 
Star Spangled Symphony 
Saturday, July 1, 8:00 p.m. Sunday, July 2, 8:00 p.m. Monday, July 3, 8:00 p.m. Tuesday, July 4, 8:00 p.m. 
Romance Under the Stars 
Friday, July 7, 8:00 p.m. Saturday, July 8, 8:00 p.m. 
John Williams Strikes Back 
Friday, July 14, 8:00 p.m. Saturday, July 15, 8:00 p.m. 
Just the Hits: 20 Years of Doo Wop Classics 
Friday, July 21, 8:00 p.m.— Scout Night presented by Printing Partners Saturday, July 22, 8:00 p.m. 
Big Bad Voodoo Daddy 
Friday, July 28, 8:00 p.m. Saturday, July 29, 8:00 p.m. 
The Beach Boys 
Friday, Aug. 4, 8:00 p.m. Saturday, Aug. 5, 8:00 p.m. 
Classical Mystery Tour: Music of the Beatles 
Friday, Aug. 11, 8:00 p.m. Saturday, Aug. 12, 8:00 p.m. 
Rumours: The Fleetwood Mac Experience 
Friday, Aug. 18, 8:00 p.m.— College and Alumni Night Saturday, Aug. 19, 8:00 p.m. 
Who's Bad: Music of Michael Jackson 
Friday, Aug. 25, 8:00 p.m.— Nurses Night Saturday, Aug. 26, 8:00 p.m. 
To Be Announced 
Thursday, Aug. 31, 8:00 p.m. Friday, Sept. 1, 8:00 p.m. 
Zoso: Music of Led Zeppelin 
Saturday, Sept. 2, 8:00 p.m. Sunday, Sept. 3, 8:00 p.m. 
10-ticket packs are on sale now; individual tickets will go on sale April 24. Click here for more information .
